WEBVTT

00:57.849 --> 00:59.934
EPISODE 15

01:00.018 --> 01:00.977
Jeong-in.

01:04.022 --> 01:05.148
Are you going to...

01:09.944 --> 01:11.112
leave us too?

01:16.618 --> 01:20.038
If that's the case,
it's still not too late.

01:23.541 --> 01:24.501
It's okay.

01:27.796 --> 01:28.838
What...

01:30.298 --> 01:31.382
What do you mean?

01:35.261 --> 01:36.221
Hey.

01:37.347 --> 01:38.681
What are you trying to say?

01:40.642 --> 01:42.018
Why are you being like this?

01:43.103 --> 01:44.479
Can I trust...

01:49.609 --> 01:50.735
how you feel about me?

01:55.865 --> 01:56.950
Tell me.

01:58.910 --> 01:59.911
Will you never...

02:03.164 --> 02:04.207
Are you sure

02:05.041 --> 02:06.835
your feelings for me will never change?

02:12.090 --> 02:13.091
Are you saying

02:14.342 --> 02:15.927
you can't trust me?

02:20.807 --> 02:22.517
I'm asking if I can trust you.

02:25.270 --> 02:26.813
Do you think I'll change?

02:28.606 --> 02:29.607
I don't know.

02:32.110 --> 02:33.778
I have no way of knowing.

02:39.200 --> 02:41.327
You're too drunk now.
Let's just talk tomorrow.

02:45.665 --> 02:47.000
You can't answer my question.

02:52.088 --> 02:53.089
I see.

03:15.361 --> 03:16.362
Jeong-in.

03:22.785 --> 03:24.537
He just drank way too much today.

03:24.621 --> 03:27.790
Please try to understand.

03:29.459 --> 03:30.710
Just today?

03:31.336 --> 03:33.004
Or will this happen again?

03:34.631 --> 03:36.341
What else does he do when he's drunk?

03:36.925 --> 03:38.301
Any other drinking behaviors?

03:41.554 --> 03:44.974
Has Ji-ho been hiding complaints about me?

03:45.058 --> 03:46.059
No, not at all.

03:46.559 --> 03:49.145
Then isn't it even more odd
that he's being like that suddenly?

03:49.771 --> 03:50.772
It's...

03:52.774 --> 03:54.859
To tell you the truth, Yu-mi...

03:56.569 --> 03:57.612
Who is that?

04:02.575 --> 04:03.576
Is she

04:04.577 --> 04:05.662
Eun-u's mom?

04:11.000 --> 04:13.670
- I don't know if I should tell you, but--
- Don't.

04:16.130 --> 04:17.298
I don't want to hear it.

04:18.800 --> 04:19.842
I'll get going.

04:32.397 --> 04:34.190
Jeong-in, what happened?

04:34.399 --> 04:36.067
- I'll call you.
- Hey.

04:36.567 --> 04:37.819
What's going on?

04:37.902 --> 04:40.238
- I said, I'll call you.
- What happened?

04:40.321 --> 04:41.531
Jeong-in.

04:42.573 --> 04:44.826
- Jeong-in, hey.
- I'm really okay.

04:45.576 --> 04:46.786
I'll call you. I'm sorry.

05:11.602 --> 05:15.106
GI-SEOK

05:26.701 --> 05:30.204
WOORI PHARMACY

06:38.231 --> 06:39.649
I drank a little at home.

06:43.111 --> 06:44.195
While I was drinking...

06:45.655 --> 06:46.739
What is this about?

06:50.952 --> 06:52.078
I just came to see you.

06:55.123 --> 06:56.916
You thought of me because you drank?

06:59.127 --> 07:00.628
Well, that can be a reason too.

07:04.048 --> 07:05.341
Where have you been?

07:06.300 --> 07:07.510
You know the answer.

07:13.224 --> 07:14.600
Can you really accept me back?

07:17.812 --> 07:19.397
I betrayed you once.

07:19.897 --> 07:21.899
Do you think you can still
get back together with me?

07:23.067 --> 07:24.444
What if I betray you again?

07:28.739 --> 07:30.324
What do you mean?

07:30.408 --> 07:31.617
Just as you heard.

07:34.203 --> 07:36.080
My feelings might change again, you know.

07:38.249 --> 07:40.585
I've done it once,
so the second time should be easier.

07:44.088 --> 07:45.214
What do you think?

07:48.384 --> 07:49.552
Can you trust me?

08:04.859 --> 08:05.693
Yes, I can.

08:38.976 --> 08:40.811
Why isn't Mr. Yu here yet?

08:41.729 --> 08:42.980
Shall I try calling him?

08:43.439 --> 08:45.525
Don't bother him. He said he'll be late.

08:49.946 --> 08:51.489
- Hello.
- Hello.

08:53.491 --> 08:54.367
Oh, no problem.

09:42.999 --> 09:45.167
YEONG-JAE

09:46.210 --> 09:48.462
- Hey.
- Are you at work?

09:50.381 --> 09:51.424
No, not yet.

09:52.091 --> 09:53.509
You drank so much last night.

09:56.887 --> 09:57.888
Last night...

09:58.806 --> 10:00.016
How did Jeong-in get home?

10:01.475 --> 10:02.768
You don't remember anything?

10:05.354 --> 10:06.981
Not everything, but...

10:08.733 --> 10:10.776
I didn't say anything weird to her, right?

10:11.360 --> 10:12.486
Have you lost your mind?

10:13.237 --> 10:15.072
You told her that you can't trust her

10:15.489 --> 10:17.992
and asked her
if she'll leave you and Eun-u.

10:19.118 --> 10:21.078
I did? I said that to Jeong-in?

10:21.162 --> 10:23.497
Then what? Would you have said that to me?

10:24.040 --> 10:28.502
She seemed to have misunderstood you,
so I actually mentioned Yu-mi--

10:28.586 --> 10:30.880
That was so unnecessary.
Why did you tell her that?

10:31.255 --> 10:33.299
I couldn't tell her
because she didn't let me.

10:33.382 --> 10:34.634
She didn't want to hear it.

10:37.803 --> 10:40.139
Why did you show it
if you wanted to hide it?

10:40.222 --> 10:41.974
You went nuts.

10:56.530 --> 10:57.615
Your phone is buzzing.

10:58.449 --> 11:00.409
- I guess the person hung up.
- Oh, thanks.

11:12.380 --> 11:15.508
You know what? The team manager
didn't like my report again.

11:15.591 --> 11:17.051
It really pissed me off,

11:17.134 --> 11:19.804
so I just tweaked a few things
and took it back to him.

11:22.139 --> 11:24.725
- He raved about it, didn't he?
- He sure did!

11:26.102 --> 11:27.687
He always does that.

11:29.980 --> 11:31.357
He caught me doing that once.

11:32.191 --> 11:33.567
Do you know what he said?

11:34.193 --> 11:35.277
"As they say,

11:35.945 --> 11:38.114
the first is always the best.

11:38.572 --> 11:41.242
The first choice you make
is always the right choice."

11:44.787 --> 11:45.996
You know him better than we do.

11:49.875 --> 11:51.085
I dealt with that many times.

12:05.224 --> 12:07.685
What? Did you think it'd be Ji-ho?

12:18.696 --> 12:20.698
You stayed up all night but came to work

12:20.823 --> 12:22.450
and even skipped lunch.

12:23.451 --> 12:24.744
So, what's the conclusion?

12:27.621 --> 12:28.956
I can't come to a conclusion.

12:30.750 --> 12:32.793
What is bothering you the most?

12:33.544 --> 12:34.920
The boy's mom?

12:35.296 --> 12:36.839
What if he's still hung up on her?

12:38.716 --> 12:39.967
That's nonsense.

12:40.968 --> 12:42.720
If he has even an ounce of feelings left,

12:42.803 --> 12:47.057
Ji-ho is... Gosh, I'd say he's so foolish.
Does he have no self-esteem?

12:49.393 --> 12:50.519
Then what about Gi-seok?

12:51.061 --> 12:52.563
That's just obsession.

12:56.066 --> 12:58.235
Ji-ho said he can't trust me,

12:59.069 --> 13:00.279
but Gi-seok said he can.

13:01.739 --> 13:03.449
Shouldn't it be the other way around?

13:05.117 --> 13:07.077
Maybe it's meant to be
the other way around.

13:07.328 --> 13:08.662
Now, you're going too far.

13:09.830 --> 13:12.208
Are you going to put the blame on Ji-ho
and run away?

13:13.667 --> 13:14.877
I'll consider that option.

13:17.171 --> 13:18.547
This one thing is clear to me.

13:20.841 --> 13:24.345
I think I only saw
what was right in front of me.

13:25.471 --> 13:26.555
But you see,

13:27.890 --> 13:30.226
knowing everything about the person's past

13:31.268 --> 13:32.895
isn't always a good thing.

13:33.687 --> 13:36.774
Sometimes, it's better to just play dumb
and let bygones be bygones.

13:38.317 --> 13:40.110
While being suspicious of each other?

13:42.446 --> 13:44.156
Ji-ho may be okay with that.

13:44.740 --> 13:47.076
But obviously not you,
knowing your personality.

14:21.861 --> 14:24.905
WOORI PHARMACY

14:32.746 --> 14:34.665
- Have a nice day.
- Thank you. You too.

14:37.126 --> 14:38.961
- Here you go.
- Thanks.

14:39.879 --> 14:41.338
- Ms. Yun Mi-sun.
- Yes.

14:43.632 --> 14:44.466
This is...

14:47.011 --> 14:48.554
- Please take them with food.
- Okay.

15:28.427 --> 15:29.470
Hey.

15:30.971 --> 15:33.015
- Let's talk somewhere else.
- What's it about?

15:45.736 --> 15:46.737
Hello?

15:47.821 --> 15:48.822
Hey, Jeong-in.

15:49.823 --> 15:50.824
Hey.

15:52.493 --> 15:54.495
I was busy, so I couldn't call you back
until now.

15:55.120 --> 15:56.080
That's okay.

15:58.499 --> 16:00.250
You got home safely last night, right?

16:05.798 --> 16:06.674
Well...

16:08.926 --> 16:10.386
For some reason, I got drunk...

16:13.806 --> 16:14.932
You're mad at me, right?

16:16.183 --> 16:17.643
I drank quite a bit last night.

16:20.020 --> 16:21.981
I know I made a mistake.
I know what I said.

16:22.773 --> 16:23.774
Well...

16:24.608 --> 16:26.568
I'm never like that though.
But yesterday...

16:27.945 --> 16:29.822
Anyway, let's meet. Let's talk in person.

16:29.905 --> 16:31.073
I can come over now.

16:32.866 --> 16:34.743
Or do you want to come over?

16:35.452 --> 16:37.955
No, let's just meet at the cafe.

16:56.557 --> 16:57.683
Hi, Mom.

16:58.475 --> 17:01.395
I told you to either come by
or call me so that I can visit you.

17:02.563 --> 17:04.481
Sorry, I've been a little busy.

17:05.691 --> 17:07.234
What's up? Did something happen?

17:07.818 --> 17:10.446
- Did Dad say something again?
- He made such a fuss.

17:11.989 --> 17:15.325
By the way, why do you sound so down?

17:16.160 --> 17:17.202
No, I'm fine.

17:18.370 --> 17:19.580
I'll see you after your class.

17:20.789 --> 17:22.666
That class ended a while ago.

17:23.250 --> 17:24.084
Oh, right.

17:26.045 --> 17:27.379
I called you to talk about...

17:28.589 --> 17:30.466
that guy.

17:30.716 --> 17:31.842
Let's talk another time.

17:32.509 --> 17:34.595
I'll come by on my day off.
We can talk then.

17:35.721 --> 17:37.222
Why wait until--

17:37.556 --> 17:40.225
Mom, I can't really talk on the phone now.

17:40.684 --> 17:42.728
I'll call you when I visit you.
I have to go.

17:54.531 --> 17:56.241
I said something foolish to Jeong-in.

17:57.034 --> 17:58.160
What did you say?

18:00.120 --> 18:02.873
Apparently, I asked her
if she's going to leave me and Eun-u.

18:04.374 --> 18:05.876
You were thinking that she might?

18:06.168 --> 18:09.004
- No, of course not.
- Then why did you talk such nonsense?

18:10.506 --> 18:13.175
You know how drunk I was last night.

18:13.759 --> 18:15.135
It's driving me nuts.

18:16.136 --> 18:18.639
You seem human for a change. Well done.

18:19.598 --> 18:20.641
What do you mean?

18:21.141 --> 18:23.685
You've been living like a robot
as though your world will be turned

18:24.144 --> 18:25.938
upside down if you let loose a little.

18:26.438 --> 18:28.649
It does make you look trustworthy,
but not human.

18:31.485 --> 18:33.821
- So that's wrong?
- It's not a good thing.

18:34.363 --> 18:36.740
What you've been showing her
isn't your bare face.

18:38.909 --> 18:39.827
Try and refute it.

18:42.246 --> 18:45.666
Well, before that...
What do I do about Jeong-in now?

18:48.836 --> 18:50.671
Even you are burdened by your past,

18:51.421 --> 18:53.924
so it must be a lot worse for Jeong-in.

18:56.093 --> 19:00.472
Don't expect her to understand everything.
That'd be the worst kind of selfishness.

19:29.126 --> 19:32.212
Do you have nothing to say?
Or is there nothing that you can say?

19:38.177 --> 19:39.386
Shall I rephrase my question?

19:41.263 --> 19:42.848
I'm asking if you have no excuse

19:43.515 --> 19:46.685
or if you can't even come up with one
because you don't remember anything.

19:51.398 --> 19:52.441
I'd say it's both.

19:57.905 --> 19:59.156
Isn't it impossible to have

19:59.865 --> 20:02.242
no recollection of anything
even if you were very drunk?

20:06.205 --> 20:08.081
I know this will sound like an excuse,

20:09.458 --> 20:11.376
but I said what I said
because I was too drunk.

20:11.460 --> 20:13.253
Do you think
I actually thought that of you?

20:13.962 --> 20:15.380
Then what did you think of me?

20:19.384 --> 20:20.594
I'm sorry.

20:22.429 --> 20:23.722
I'm truly sorry.

20:24.890 --> 20:27.851
But I've never once thought
you'd do such a thing.

20:28.268 --> 20:29.311
I'm serious.

20:31.188 --> 20:32.898
Leaving me and Eun-u...

20:34.858 --> 20:36.610
I'm too embarrassed to even bring it up.

20:37.778 --> 20:40.280
I've never even imagined
doing such a thing.

20:42.199 --> 20:43.200
See?

20:44.201 --> 20:45.244
But the thing is,

20:48.163 --> 20:49.873
you asked if I, too, would leave you.

20:51.959 --> 20:55.295
"Are you going to leave us too?"
That was your question.

20:59.383 --> 21:00.968
I know that I'm nitpicking.

21:01.760 --> 21:03.303
I may be reading too much into it.

21:05.514 --> 21:07.683
But to be honest,
the impression I got from it was...

21:10.394 --> 21:12.896
"Aren't you just like her?"
That's what it sounded like.

21:18.527 --> 21:20.195
I know you didn't mean it that way.

21:20.988 --> 21:22.948
Like I said,
it's just the impression I got.

21:28.829 --> 21:30.247
I never thought

21:31.790 --> 21:33.458
your wound must've completely healed

21:34.626 --> 21:37.087
just because some time has passed.

21:39.506 --> 21:42.092
Even so, I can't just put it behind me
thinking that it is

21:42.801 --> 21:45.262
something you said unwittingly
because you were drunk.

21:48.807 --> 21:50.434
I don't know how I can...

21:53.979 --> 21:55.105
This is so...

21:56.023 --> 21:59.234
This is so frustrating for me
because I don't remember everything.

22:00.777 --> 22:02.529
That's why I can't even give an excuse,

22:03.405 --> 22:05.240
try to refute it, or apologize properly.

22:05.866 --> 22:08.327
I don't even know where to begin
to apologize to you.

22:10.370 --> 22:12.205
What if it leads
to more misunderstandings?

22:14.624 --> 22:16.501
It's seriously driving me nuts.

22:18.378 --> 22:19.671
I don't want an apology.

22:20.881 --> 22:21.882
Hold on.

22:24.051 --> 22:25.594
Like you said,

22:27.888 --> 22:31.475
no matter how hard I try not to be
bogged down by my past and scars,

22:32.100 --> 22:33.643
I can't help feeling insecure.

22:35.103 --> 22:37.606
The anxiety that I didn't even know I had
came out. That's all.

22:37.689 --> 22:38.982
There's nothing more to it.

22:42.402 --> 22:43.403
That's how I am too.

22:44.863 --> 22:46.823
I betrayed my boyfriend,

22:47.532 --> 22:49.493
and you witnessed the whole thing.

22:51.161 --> 22:54.039
- Now, you're going too far.
- I feel insecure, just like you do.

22:55.374 --> 22:56.416
I know

22:57.334 --> 23:00.295
that you don't completely distrust me.
I know that,

23:01.963 --> 23:03.256
but even though I know that...

23:05.217 --> 23:06.510
I can't help feeling uneasy.

23:15.185 --> 23:17.479
I wish I could open up my heart
and show you.

23:19.940 --> 23:22.484
I tried to push you away
thinking you're too good for me.

23:23.276 --> 23:26.696
And that woman went through
all that trouble just to be with me.

23:27.531 --> 23:29.574
How could I have doubted
your feelings for me?

23:34.413 --> 23:35.664
Not you.

23:37.499 --> 23:38.959
I'm doubting myself.

23:42.003 --> 23:43.171
I told you

23:44.381 --> 23:46.007
that I coveted you.

23:47.676 --> 23:50.011
I know you thought about pushing me away,

23:51.138 --> 23:53.014
but I only thought I couldn't let you go.

23:55.308 --> 23:56.518
Perhaps I jumped into this

23:58.728 --> 24:00.605
way too quickly because of my greed.

24:17.205 --> 24:18.165
Hi.

24:19.207 --> 24:21.376
Assemblyman Jang
wants to have dinner with us.

24:25.338 --> 24:29.050
Hey, it's not like she's the only woman
in the world.

24:29.718 --> 24:32.596
Move on already. Don't be a clingy loser.

24:33.054 --> 24:34.222
I need to redeem myself,

24:35.599 --> 24:36.808
so I'm not ready yet.

24:37.809 --> 24:38.852
"Yet"?

24:39.644 --> 24:41.313
I guess you've decided to move on.

24:44.065 --> 24:45.192
It won't take long.

24:46.151 --> 24:49.237
As for the dinner with Assemblyman Jang,
try to postpone it a little.

24:51.323 --> 24:53.033
Are you open to meeting his daughter?

24:56.495 --> 24:57.787
Why not?

24:59.456 --> 25:01.666
It'll depend on how things
get sorted out though.

25:06.671 --> 25:08.840
What can I do to make you forgive me?

25:11.885 --> 25:13.678
I told you. The problem is me, not you.

25:15.305 --> 25:18.475
I'm not just saying it
to make you feel worse.

25:21.770 --> 25:22.854
I love you.

25:26.107 --> 25:27.984
I thought our love was all that mattered.

25:29.236 --> 25:32.239
I cluelessly thought I should be able
to understand everything...

25:33.698 --> 25:34.699
No.

25:36.243 --> 25:39.579
I didn't even think.
I just assumed everything would work out.

25:45.710 --> 25:46.711
But...

25:48.213 --> 25:49.881
even though you brought up your past

25:52.092 --> 25:53.885
only for a short moment,

25:55.011 --> 25:56.179
my heart sank.

25:57.931 --> 26:00.225
As if I encountered
what I've been trying to avoid.

26:02.686 --> 26:03.812
That's why I realized...

26:06.690 --> 26:07.774
my feelings

26:09.317 --> 26:10.527
may not be there yet.

26:15.073 --> 26:16.408
Regardless of the situation,

26:17.534 --> 26:19.411
whenever you catch your own shortcoming,

26:20.120 --> 26:21.621
you want to run from it at first.

26:23.915 --> 26:25.041
That's how I feel now.

26:31.423 --> 26:34.801
I think I need some time
to reflect on myself.

26:37.429 --> 26:39.055
I know I could let it slide,

26:39.222 --> 26:41.558
and you may resent me
for not being understanding,

26:43.393 --> 26:44.436
but I'm sorry.

26:46.521 --> 26:49.024
I know I can lie,
but I can't even do that now.

26:51.276 --> 26:52.736
I don't want to act cool

26:53.862 --> 26:54.988
or act like I'm okay.

26:56.323 --> 26:57.907
I don't want you to do that either.

27:01.703 --> 27:02.704
You're right.

27:05.040 --> 27:06.750
I've been fooling myself and others,

27:09.419 --> 27:11.296
not because I'm still hung up on my past,

27:13.173 --> 27:14.341
but because of my fear.

27:17.135 --> 27:18.928
It's a fact that I can't deny.

27:21.139 --> 27:22.599
Still, I can't--

27:22.682 --> 27:24.768
I'm not saying
I don't understand how you feel.

27:28.271 --> 27:30.106
Then you probably know how I feel now.

27:32.609 --> 27:34.486
You must also know what I want to say.

27:39.115 --> 27:40.158
Lee Jeong-in.

27:43.078 --> 27:45.205
I'll say it again
now that I'm completely sober.

27:47.707 --> 27:48.708
Don't...

27:50.126 --> 27:51.211
leave us.

30:39.212 --> 30:40.255
Hello?

30:41.047 --> 30:42.006
Dad.

30:43.758 --> 30:44.759
Yes.

30:45.760 --> 30:47.136
When are you coming, Dad?

30:51.140 --> 30:52.600
When will you come home?

30:55.937 --> 30:56.938
Come soon.

30:59.607 --> 31:01.985
Okay, I'll come now.

31:32.473 --> 31:34.017
I was surprised too.

31:35.226 --> 31:37.103
She actually consoled me.

31:40.315 --> 31:42.233
"Would I be able to do that
if I were her?"

31:43.359 --> 31:45.570
That was all I could think
on my way back home.

31:47.405 --> 31:50.074
Your dad didn't even believe me
when I told him.

31:51.200 --> 31:53.036
How could anyone believe that?

31:53.119 --> 31:57.415
I never talked about it,
but I was very worried as well.

31:59.250 --> 32:01.419
How could she be so understanding
and kind?

32:03.504 --> 32:05.924
You have to thank her.

32:08.760 --> 32:11.346
At a time like this, you should really try
to be more confident.

32:11.429 --> 32:13.348
She chose to be with you
because she trusts you.

32:13.431 --> 32:14.682
You have to look dependable.

32:20.188 --> 32:21.648
What's with that reaction?

32:23.399 --> 32:24.233
It's nothing.

32:25.318 --> 32:28.029
I'm sure he's more surprised than we were.

32:38.665 --> 32:39.666
Dad.

32:40.750 --> 32:43.044
- Yes?
- Ms. Lee.

32:44.837 --> 32:45.880
You should go to sleep.

32:46.589 --> 32:49.801
Can we go out with Ms. Lee again?

32:51.844 --> 32:54.639
Okay. Go to sleep now.

33:30.383 --> 33:32.719
- You can take this.
- It's okay. You drink that.

33:37.557 --> 33:39.434
By the way, how's Ji-ho doing?

33:40.852 --> 33:42.103
He's doing pretty well.

33:43.396 --> 33:44.522
He's doing well?

33:46.315 --> 33:47.316
Yes.

33:49.110 --> 33:50.319
I see.

33:52.071 --> 33:53.156
You knew about it?

34:00.163 --> 34:01.205
Sort of.

34:03.207 --> 34:04.292
Who told you?

34:05.168 --> 34:06.252
Did Jeong-in tell you?

34:26.064 --> 34:30.026
Be there for your buddy.
He already had it tough to begin with.

35:12.068 --> 35:13.152
Mom.

35:17.281 --> 35:20.243
Why do you look so weary?

35:20.535 --> 35:21.536
Nothing. I'm fine.

35:22.286 --> 35:24.789
I'm sorry. I was going to come by,
but work's been busy.

35:25.581 --> 35:27.875
I'm not here
because I got tired of waiting.

35:29.043 --> 35:31.963
Are you feeling sick or something?

35:32.505 --> 35:33.506
No, I'm fine.

35:34.549 --> 35:36.592
Wait here. I'll go get some coffee for us.

35:40.847 --> 35:42.890
I don't know
if this is the right thing to do.

35:44.183 --> 35:47.895
To tell you the truth, I'm still not sure.

35:53.609 --> 35:57.864
But you say
that you can't be happy without him,

35:58.781 --> 36:00.324
so nothing else should matter.

36:04.537 --> 36:07.623
I haven't been properly
introduced to him yet,

36:09.125 --> 36:11.085
but meeting his mom
told me a lot about him.

36:17.049 --> 36:19.260
You still have to jump over many hurdles.

36:21.721 --> 36:23.139
Marriage won't be the end.

36:26.893 --> 36:30.271
It'll be harder
than what you're expecting.

36:35.151 --> 36:37.612
There may come a time
when you'll regret your decision.

36:42.700 --> 36:44.076
Gosh, my goodness.

36:45.161 --> 36:48.372
Someone might think
you're crying because you're upset.

36:56.714 --> 37:00.509
I know this whole ordeal
hasn't been easy for you.

37:02.845 --> 37:05.014
But you'll still need to go through hoops.

37:06.974 --> 37:10.561
My approval alone is only the beginning.

37:13.564 --> 37:14.523
I know.

37:17.652 --> 37:18.653
Hold on.

37:20.863 --> 37:21.906
There's...

37:23.366 --> 37:24.700
something wrong, isn't there?

37:31.082 --> 37:32.416
I'm just happy, that's all.

37:33.542 --> 37:34.585
I'm happy, Mom.

37:51.852 --> 37:53.062
Thank you.

37:55.856 --> 37:57.024
Your dad

37:58.150 --> 38:00.236
never listens to me anyway,

38:00.903 --> 38:03.155
so you two should
talk this through yourselves.

38:04.448 --> 38:05.825
Don't be mean to him though.

38:06.534 --> 38:07.660
What?

38:07.743 --> 38:10.413
Because of his situation,

38:10.496 --> 38:12.498
he won't be able to speak confidently.

38:13.291 --> 38:14.292
That's not the case.

38:14.959 --> 38:16.168
Of course, it is.

38:17.086 --> 38:19.130
You're no better than him.

38:19.422 --> 38:21.132
Between you two, you lack more.

38:21.757 --> 38:22.758
How so?

38:23.259 --> 38:26.053
Do you know what it's like to be a parent?

38:27.471 --> 38:29.598
The biggest lesson in life

38:30.016 --> 38:31.809
is taught when you raise kids.

38:33.185 --> 38:35.062
He's maturer than you are.

38:38.983 --> 38:40.026
What was that?

38:41.777 --> 38:42.737
Nothing.

38:48.993 --> 38:49.994
Goodness.

39:12.850 --> 39:14.518
You can head home if you have plans.

39:22.109 --> 39:23.194
I don't.

39:26.697 --> 39:27.740
I really don't.

39:32.244 --> 39:34.288
He's back to his old self again.

39:36.957 --> 39:38.000
Don't.

39:43.798 --> 39:45.216
I knew you'd give me that look.

39:47.009 --> 39:49.345
My sister called it quits first?

39:51.013 --> 39:53.015
It's better to say they're on a break.

39:53.516 --> 39:58.437
Ji-ho's insecurity that he wasn't aware of
came bursting out,

39:58.521 --> 40:02.316
and Jeong-in took it the wrong way.

40:03.442 --> 40:05.403
So? What did Ji-ho say?

40:06.237 --> 40:08.239
Nothing. He's just depressed.

40:08.614 --> 40:09.990
He feels ashamed.

40:10.783 --> 40:12.284
And he's going to stay that way?

40:12.785 --> 40:15.788
What can he do?
It's all up to Jeong-in now.

40:16.872 --> 40:20.042
Jeez, they're one and the same.

40:20.626 --> 40:21.669
What do you mean?

40:22.837 --> 40:25.005
My sister has experienced
enough trauma herself.

40:28.175 --> 40:29.468
What do you think will happen?

40:30.845 --> 40:33.556
I, of course, understand Ji-ho,

40:34.348 --> 40:36.684
but I get why Jeong-in is upset too.

40:43.357 --> 40:44.650
We should call it quits too.

40:48.946 --> 40:50.239
You're his friend, remember?

40:50.990 --> 40:53.325
I can't be disloyal to my sister.

40:54.160 --> 40:55.161
What?

40:55.494 --> 40:57.830
It's our family motto.
You have a problem with that?

40:58.080 --> 41:00.207
Why do they dictate our relationship?

41:00.291 --> 41:01.375
It does in my book.

41:04.712 --> 41:06.338
This is totally absurd.

41:10.050 --> 41:11.302
Why is that though?

41:27.776 --> 41:28.861
Hold on.

41:29.820 --> 41:32.865
I thought the sudden invite
would entail backup.

41:32.948 --> 41:34.200
Not even Jae-in's home.

41:35.451 --> 41:36.577
What's going on?

41:37.912 --> 41:40.247
I didn't want her to hear us,

41:40.456 --> 41:42.041
so I told her to give us space.

41:47.963 --> 41:49.548
My mouth hurts from repeating this.

41:52.384 --> 41:53.761
I won't divorce you.

41:56.430 --> 41:57.556
Our divorce...

41:59.016 --> 42:00.267
is inevitable.

42:00.351 --> 42:03.938
All that's left is whether
you'll just end up a divorcé

42:04.021 --> 42:05.523
who gave up his paternal rights

42:07.233 --> 42:08.317
or be charged with assault--

42:08.400 --> 42:10.069
- Hey.
- I'm not finished.

42:11.487 --> 42:12.780
On top of that,

42:16.033 --> 42:18.244
I can charge you
with sexual assault as well.

42:21.121 --> 42:22.206
The choice is yours.

42:29.713 --> 42:31.006
Must I patronize you again?

42:33.175 --> 42:35.719
Think about after the baby is born.

42:37.179 --> 42:38.639
Would it like a criminal for a dad?

42:38.722 --> 42:40.224
Could you say it shamelessly?

42:40.307 --> 42:42.101
Waver my paternal rights?

42:42.184 --> 42:43.936
You're basically asking us
to deny each other.

42:44.019 --> 42:46.063
Tell me if that's even possible.

42:48.274 --> 42:49.692
It can be from the heart.

42:51.527 --> 42:54.029
Once the kid grows up
to tell what's right from wrong,

42:55.614 --> 42:57.074
it'll deny your existence.

43:02.246 --> 43:03.414
This is your last chance.

43:05.040 --> 43:08.252
Fill out the divorce papers
and bring them to me.

43:09.712 --> 43:11.797
Leave. Leave already!

43:16.510 --> 43:17.469
Must I call the cops?

43:18.679 --> 43:20.848
Okay, fine. Let's get a divorce.

43:22.016 --> 43:23.100
I'll agree to it.

43:25.102 --> 43:26.854
I'm the one divorcing you, you prick.

43:27.605 --> 43:29.815
Right, whatever.

43:31.275 --> 43:32.776
But not until the baby is born.

43:35.070 --> 43:36.113
Haven't you...

43:38.907 --> 43:40.367
heard of prenatal education?

43:41.410 --> 43:43.037
I'm only looking out for you.

43:43.996 --> 43:45.372
Cut the bullshit.

43:47.541 --> 43:50.210
You have no right to see this baby.
Now, let go.

44:13.108 --> 44:15.110
8 P.M. TIME OF LOVE

44:25.788 --> 44:28.123
Tell Seo-in I'll be over next week.

44:30.000 --> 44:32.127
Shouldn't Ji-ho be a priority?

44:36.965 --> 44:38.384
Your acting has gotten better.

44:41.220 --> 44:42.554
I need time to think.

44:42.971 --> 44:44.223
You're better at lying too.

44:44.640 --> 44:46.642
Why think
when he's taken over your thoughts?

44:48.102 --> 44:49.186
You should get going.

44:49.978 --> 44:53.190
This is why those who've been hurt
can be harsher.

44:54.274 --> 44:55.567
What are you babbling on about?

44:56.026 --> 44:57.986
When Gi-seok's father disapproved of you,

44:58.070 --> 44:59.655
your pride was wounded deeply.

45:00.072 --> 45:01.949
Ji-ho's in a tougher spot,

45:02.491 --> 45:04.368
but you're turning your back on him
as well.

45:05.327 --> 45:08.080
I was just as wounded by him too.

45:08.455 --> 45:09.790
I'm self-reflecting as it is,

45:10.124 --> 45:12.376
but how could I not
be annoyed by those words?

45:12.793 --> 45:14.086
I'm not spineless, you know.

45:16.797 --> 45:19.842
All right, fine.
Continue to be like that then.

45:33.856 --> 45:35.232
Why not just resign?

45:38.026 --> 45:40.195
For the first time,
I've started to hate my job.

45:42.573 --> 45:45.659
People always ask me twice
to confirm what my job is,

45:47.453 --> 45:49.538
and I can't afford to make any mistakes.

45:53.083 --> 45:55.043
It's not like I can
break free from that routine.

45:55.127 --> 45:56.044
It's...

45:56.920 --> 45:58.464
It's just what my life is like.

46:04.136 --> 46:05.971
The thought just came to me that's all.

46:06.430 --> 46:09.850
No one's stopping you, but yourself.

46:10.392 --> 46:11.894
I didn't mean it like that.

46:19.485 --> 46:20.444
What?

46:20.861 --> 46:23.906
Are you and Jeong-in over?
As in completely?

46:25.282 --> 46:28.243
- What now?
- Even Gi-seok knows.

46:30.287 --> 46:32.831
I can't believe her.
Did she already tell him?

46:34.124 --> 46:35.542
Are they getting back together?

46:39.046 --> 46:40.380
I'm heading out for a moment.

46:42.049 --> 46:43.050
No.

46:47.095 --> 46:48.388
I said you can't.

46:55.979 --> 46:57.022
Ji-ho.

47:17.876 --> 47:19.419
This is a surprise.

47:20.671 --> 47:22.923
I'd like to talk. Can we meet?

47:27.469 --> 47:30.639
I'm afraid I have plans tonight.

47:33.183 --> 47:36.395
Maybe next time.
I'll call you when I have the time.

47:36.478 --> 47:38.230
I'm downstairs. It won't take long.

48:00.794 --> 48:01.753
Hey.

48:02.421 --> 48:03.839
Why are you here at this hour?

48:06.049 --> 48:07.968
I'm not here for you, so get back to work.

48:08.427 --> 48:09.553
Gi-seok then?

48:10.137 --> 48:11.388
Is it because I called?

48:13.640 --> 48:16.894
I was only rambling.
I don't even know if it's true or not.

48:20.397 --> 48:22.858
Don't cause any trouble, all right?

48:39.082 --> 48:41.418
- Hello.
- Jeez.

48:44.880 --> 48:47.299
You must be quite desperate

48:47.758 --> 48:49.092
to seek me out like this.

48:56.975 --> 48:58.101
Well, go on and talk.

49:07.444 --> 49:08.528
I told you before

49:10.113 --> 49:11.323
to let Jeong-in be.

49:13.200 --> 49:14.368
Who says I did anything?

49:15.494 --> 49:16.620
Did Hyeon-su say so?

49:19.831 --> 49:22.834
What can I do
to cut you out from her life?

49:25.754 --> 49:27.214
You know,

49:28.465 --> 49:29.716
you should watch what you say.

49:30.008 --> 49:33.011
I said before that
I will only let it slide once.

49:34.346 --> 49:35.347
Have you forgotten that?

49:36.765 --> 49:40.143
You sure have a bad memory
for someone who's smart.

49:40.227 --> 49:41.520
I told you...

49:42.229 --> 49:44.606
that I'd give up if you do as well.

49:47.609 --> 49:48.777
Do you think you can

49:50.153 --> 49:52.364
get back together with Jeong-in
if I give up?

49:55.492 --> 49:56.618
I never said I would.

50:22.936 --> 50:24.438
Yu Ji-ho, you bastard.

50:33.655 --> 50:34.698
What?

50:35.490 --> 50:36.992
Why do you seem startled?

50:38.660 --> 50:39.703
You know me.

50:40.871 --> 50:42.414
My goal is taking you down.

50:44.583 --> 50:45.584
Still,

50:46.585 --> 50:49.504
I'd likely take Jeong-in
if she came back to me.

50:50.047 --> 50:51.673
I was going to marry her after all.

50:54.092 --> 50:56.553
It's a way of giving back to our parents

50:56.636 --> 50:58.180
who still want us to marry.

50:58.847 --> 51:02.017
There'd be nothing bad about any of it.

51:07.105 --> 51:08.440
You don't know her.

51:09.441 --> 51:10.609
She isn't the type

51:11.777 --> 51:13.695
to be satisfied with just love.

51:15.530 --> 51:18.283
Look who she dated for all this time.

51:18.366 --> 51:19.785
Doesn't it tell you anything?

51:22.329 --> 51:23.789
You won't be able to handle her.

51:27.209 --> 51:29.044
Your crappy romance

51:30.295 --> 51:32.255
isn't anywhere up to her level.

51:40.806 --> 51:41.973
Do I seem like a bastard?

51:44.226 --> 51:45.977
I became this way because of her.

51:50.982 --> 51:53.777
This is how I turned out to be,
but for you...

51:57.030 --> 51:58.657
I feel terrible for you.

51:59.950 --> 52:01.368
Your future is already drawn.

52:14.422 --> 52:17.050
If you're truly concerned about me,
then thanks.

52:19.261 --> 52:20.971
What I'll say now isn't a warning.

52:22.264 --> 52:23.223
It's a threat.

52:29.479 --> 52:31.731
You're just as smart,
so I'm sure you'll remember.

52:33.233 --> 52:35.277
I said I would let other things slide,

52:35.360 --> 52:37.279
but not when it concerns my son.

52:40.949 --> 52:42.576
This again?

52:44.077 --> 52:45.328
Don't you realize

52:46.580 --> 52:50.584
that your son
is one of your worst weaknesses?

52:51.084 --> 52:54.087
When put to good use,
it can be my biggest weapon.

52:55.881 --> 52:57.132
The photos you illegally took

52:58.425 --> 52:59.676
of me and my son.

53:01.553 --> 53:02.929
How should I utilize that?

53:07.559 --> 53:09.811
From what I hear,
your father had them taken.

53:14.232 --> 53:16.568
I let it slide at the time
because of Jeong-in's sake.

53:16.651 --> 53:18.570
It's not because I'm spineless.

53:22.073 --> 53:23.241
Are you challenging

53:24.159 --> 53:26.077
my father of all people?

53:26.661 --> 53:28.330
Like I said, I'm not scared of anything.

53:29.331 --> 53:31.416
I'm never scared when it comes to my boy.

54:10.914 --> 54:13.166
HOW TO PREPARE FOR HAPPY LATER YEARS

54:22.384 --> 54:23.551
Oh, hi, Gi-seok.

54:23.927 --> 54:27.389
Hi, it's me.
I'm sorry for not being in touch.

54:27.764 --> 54:30.100
It's fine. I know you're just as busy.

54:30.767 --> 54:34.104
Could you perhaps
spare me some time tonight?

54:35.188 --> 54:36.231
Why is that?

54:36.898 --> 54:38.525
Is there something to talk about?

54:39.067 --> 54:40.068
Of course.

54:40.819 --> 54:44.155
You said you'd settle on a date
for me and Jeong-in.

54:46.491 --> 54:47.534
Sir?

54:47.993 --> 54:50.078
Oh, right.

54:50.161 --> 54:53.206
A wedding date, of course.
I should settle on one.

54:53.790 --> 54:56.418
All right.
When and where should we meet today?

54:57.460 --> 54:58.920
- Take care.
- Bye.

55:00.880 --> 55:03.341
WOORI PHARMACY

55:03.425 --> 55:04.509
Welcome.

55:06.970 --> 55:07.971
Excuse me.

55:09.431 --> 55:11.349
What can I get you?

55:12.100 --> 55:14.436
- Hello.
- Hi, it's been a while.

55:15.270 --> 55:17.063
Ji-ho isn't in at the moment.

55:19.482 --> 55:20.400
I see.

55:21.192 --> 55:23.361
- Goodbye then.
- Would you like a cup of tea?

55:23.445 --> 55:25.363
No, I'm good, but thanks for the offer.

55:25.905 --> 55:26.865
Take care then.

55:45.467 --> 55:48.678
Right. Well, I'm heading out as we speak,

55:48.845 --> 55:54.351
so you can leave in about 20 minutes.

55:55.185 --> 55:56.853
The timing would be right.

55:57.979 --> 56:00.774
Sure thing. I'll see you later.

56:28.009 --> 56:30.553
Is Mr. Kwon still here?

56:30.970 --> 56:33.056
Yes, he had some business to take care of.

56:33.556 --> 56:34.849
I see.

56:36.643 --> 56:37.811
There he comes.

56:42.482 --> 56:44.984
- What are you still doing here?
- I'm on my way out too.

56:45.693 --> 56:47.070
How's the injury?

56:47.445 --> 56:49.739
I'm fine. It's only a sprain.

56:49.989 --> 56:51.199
You should get going then.

56:52.575 --> 56:53.868
Do you have any plans today?

56:54.661 --> 56:56.329
I'm sorry, but I'm meeting someone.

56:56.621 --> 56:58.873
Did you have something to tell me?

56:59.416 --> 57:01.000
Is it just me who have things to say?

57:02.460 --> 57:04.462
- All right. You can get going.
- Sure.

57:28.445 --> 57:29.737
What do you want for dinner?

57:30.238 --> 57:32.907
They have everything here, just name it.

57:36.119 --> 57:37.120
What's wrong?

57:38.746 --> 57:39.831
I'll take a rain check.

57:40.331 --> 57:41.791
But you came all the way here.

57:42.500 --> 57:45.086
All right, fine.
I won't ask you what happened.

57:45.962 --> 57:48.590
That's not it.
I should hurry back to the pharmacy.

57:50.175 --> 57:52.385
It's close to closing time anyway.

57:53.219 --> 57:55.763
Still. Besides, I'm not even hungry.

57:57.724 --> 57:58.808
I'll see you around.

58:03.980 --> 58:05.398
Are you that hungry?

58:05.482 --> 58:07.901
This is more than what two people can eat.

58:09.527 --> 58:11.696
I thought it'd help you recover faster.

58:13.990 --> 58:15.783
Then don't cause me any problems.

58:17.869 --> 58:19.537
I wanted to apologize too.

58:24.792 --> 58:27.420
Anyway, Jeong-in's done with wandering.

58:30.757 --> 58:34.052
What did I tell you?
She just pitied him, that's all.

58:35.678 --> 58:37.764
Is she coming back to you then?

58:39.182 --> 58:40.475
That's up to you.

58:42.810 --> 58:44.771
Decide on a position for her father.

58:44.854 --> 58:45.980
Are you serious?

58:51.486 --> 58:52.820
Sir, you're here.

58:57.283 --> 58:59.911
What's going on?

59:00.286 --> 59:01.663
Well...

59:02.288 --> 59:05.083
I didn't realize that
I'd set an appointment on the same day.

59:05.166 --> 59:08.127
I only figured it out once I arrived here.

59:08.211 --> 59:12.257
I was going to call,
but you'd probably be on your way so...

59:13.341 --> 59:14.801
Please have a seat first.

59:15.468 --> 59:16.511
Right.

59:17.387 --> 59:18.513
Here you go.

59:21.516 --> 59:23.518
Will you excuse me for a moment?

59:44.122 --> 59:45.540
Was this your plan for tonight?

59:47.208 --> 59:49.335
Why didn't you tell me
you were meeting my son?

59:53.339 --> 59:56.593
All these years,
I've learned what to talk about and not.

01:00:08.062 --> 01:00:09.772
Ye-seul, I'm sorry I'm late.

01:00:10.106 --> 01:00:11.983
- Was it busy today?
- Yes.

01:00:13.192 --> 01:00:14.736
I see. I'm sorry.

01:00:16.029 --> 01:00:18.072
It's fine. I'll see you tomorrow.

01:00:26.789 --> 01:00:30.543
- I'm sorry. I met Ye-seul outside and--
- This is a place of work, you know.

01:00:32.253 --> 01:00:33.254
I apologize.

01:00:33.963 --> 01:00:35.798
I can only be understanding to a point.

01:00:36.424 --> 01:00:38.051
Don't you think this was selfish?

01:00:40.428 --> 01:00:41.429
Hye-jeong...

01:00:43.097 --> 01:00:44.724
Do better, all right?

01:00:45.975 --> 01:00:47.226
Lock up well.

01:00:58.154 --> 01:00:59.906
We did it!

01:01:14.962 --> 01:01:16.089
What are you doing here?

01:01:18.383 --> 01:01:19.550
Where were you today?

01:01:31.854 --> 01:01:33.189
Where were you?

01:01:36.442 --> 01:01:38.403
I had somewhere to be.

01:01:40.613 --> 01:01:41.739
You must be at ease

01:01:42.990 --> 01:01:44.200
to run errands like this.

01:01:49.080 --> 01:01:50.873
Let's go. We'll talk somewhere else.

01:01:51.666 --> 01:01:52.709
About what?

01:01:54.460 --> 01:01:55.586
Aren't you here to talk?

01:01:56.421 --> 01:01:57.422
I'm not.

01:01:59.674 --> 01:02:00.758
Then why are you here?

01:02:04.011 --> 01:02:05.054
To buy medicine.

01:02:06.472 --> 01:02:07.515
What kind?

01:02:12.687 --> 01:02:13.730
What is it?

01:02:16.023 --> 01:02:17.692
A medicine that can cure

01:02:18.526 --> 01:02:20.153
the need to smack someone

01:02:21.237 --> 01:02:23.364
and a truly worried and upset heart.

01:02:29.245 --> 01:02:30.580
Forget it if you've got none.

01:03:26.761 --> 01:03:29.388
Gi-seok probably has
skeletons in his closet too.

01:03:29.472 --> 01:03:32.767
If I had known about this,
I would've taken photos too.

01:03:32.850 --> 01:03:34.644
Are you challenging me?

01:03:34.727 --> 01:03:36.687
- I'm done serving you!
- Are you insane?

01:03:36.771 --> 01:03:40.942
What do you mean
Yu Ji-ho isn't a decent man?

01:03:41.025 --> 01:03:43.528
He threatened me
with the photos that were taken.

01:03:43.611 --> 01:03:45.238
He could be after money.

01:03:45.321 --> 01:03:47.615
My mom wants to meet you, Ji-ho.

01:03:47.782 --> 01:03:49.283
I'd like to bring Eun-u, too.

01:03:49.408 --> 01:03:52.078
I should've thought of that first.
Sure, let's do that.

01:03:52.161 --> 01:03:54.372
I like it that you think
this is our decision.

01:03:54.455 --> 01:03:56.624
What do you say
to being a director after retirement?

01:03:56.707 --> 01:03:58.334
I appreciate the offer,

01:03:58.417 --> 01:04:00.461
but I'd like some time to think about it.

01:04:00.962 --> 01:04:01.838
Are you still sulking?

01:04:01.921 --> 01:04:04.006
Is there no chance
for you and Gi-seok anymore?

01:04:04.090 --> 01:04:05.758
Just be patient with me, Dad.

01:04:05.842 --> 01:04:07.468
You'll soon see me live a happy life.

01:04:08.427 --> 01:04:09.554
Please believe in me.

01:04:12.098 --> 01:04:14.392
Subtitle translation by Liya Choi
